repasa is a set of three kind of tools: For creation of contents 
directly in the XML format of repasa or in other file formats 
(DocBook and LaTeX) following some conventions, for checking the 
contents, and for studying the contents and registering progress. 
The contents can be specified with definitions, classifications for the 
definitions (possibly along with exercises), and sequences of study. 
It is especially well suited to organize information according to the 
current legislation for education in schools of Colombia.

